# SECURITY: this repo is Josh's personal knowledge vault (raw/, wiki/, ops/
# contain — or will contain — personal finance and health material). Only the
# dashboard app itself should ever be publicly deployed. Allowlist, not a
# denylist, on purpose: a denylist silently stops protecting the moment a new
# top-level folder is added; this fails closed instead.
